{"tid":2290880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：正研究豁免隔離由「居大陸香港居民」擴至「大灣區居民」","createTime":"2020-11-18T10:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:20:35.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9d8591079bc6e6386a6119fcb98ae385888dc6","tid":2290880,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"消息：政府研究安排粵澳居民來港豁免強制檢疫<br />\n<br />\n身處內地及澳門的香港居民由下周一起，可透過「回港易」制度返港而毋須在住所強制檢疫14日，今日起接受預約。消息指，政府正積極研究，是否可以擴大計劃至從廣東省或澳門來港的居民，都可以豁免強制檢疫14天，但仍然要視乎疫情發展，而即使落實，他們返回當地仍要隔離2星期。<br />\n<br />\n「回港易」申請系統隨後會逢星期三至星期五開放，接受下個星期一至星期日七天期間返港的預約，最多可為三名同行的香港居民提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2366840&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=b069a0b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2366840</a>"},{"pid":"28433b9de6bbec1e6f94d40c3a16ebfc8b3fb4e4","tid":2290880,"uid":51820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦 你講晒嫁啦"},{"pid":"0d20d0f455d82b255566486f9c175f7b8b32028a","tid":2290880,"uid":249960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"大陸雞返嚟啦"},{"pid":"1d839698e03c3f85a1bad0eea7d78743dfc90b89","tid":2290880,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:50:55.000Z","msg":"拆關卡算啦"},{"pid":"61c80856030729b8ced4c89e7c6a3462e12b646f","tid":2290880,"uid":189046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"想自殺冇人阻到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7aae075eb41465705c55cf8bce009bd28f61068","tid":2290880,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fe5945a5c3509723eb8e28ecc24fa9dbe1cbc5","tid":22908